Description:
Cannock Chase District Council and Stafford Borough Council are looking to procure the services of a consultant with experience in Environmental Services to undertake a joint review of both Councils Environmental Services to:

•	Analyse and benchmark the current services;
•	Recommend the most appropriate service delivery model(s);
•	Identify savings that can be achieved.

This is considered to be a significant piece of work for both Councils and will shape future service delivery.

Further details on the work required are given in the specification. Full instructions for both completing, and submitting, can be found at https://supplierlive.proactisp2p.com/Account/Login
